	(uuid "a0727808-af70-4056-b2ee-ab828c2acfbd")
	(paper "A4")
	(title_block
		(title "PET/CBM \"N\" Keyboard")
		(date "2025-10-05")
		(rev "N-V3-R0")
		(company "Steve J. Gray, André Fachat")
	)
	(lib_symbols)
	(text "1. Original:\n   No ICs/LEDs/Capacitors/Oscillator\n   Use original single row 20pin connector\n   Solder Jumpers JP1, JP2, and JC1..JC8\n\n2. Full uPET with key scanner and LEDs:\n   All SMD parts (ICs, capacitors, LEDs, ...)\n   Use 20pin IDC (2row) connector\n   Requires 3.3V and 5V supply and I2C for control\n\n3. IDC connector without key scanner/LEDs\n   Only use U7 (4-to-10 mapper), C9, C33\n   Use 20pin IDC (2row) connector\n   Requires 5V power supply only\n   Solder Jumpers JC1..JC8"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 29.21 106.68 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 2.54 2.54)
				(thickness 0.6)
				(bold yes)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "0435caf2-9c4d-4d2c-8670-0dfb03a51053")
	)
	(text "R3.0A:\n- add LED and keyboard controllers, and LED backlights\nR3.0B:\n- Temporarily Fix off-by-one on U7, Connect clock \n  oscillator to supply voltage"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 168.148 149.098 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 2.54 2.54)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "2503191f-1565-4414-9368-ff727eeba59e")
	)
	(text "All SMD parts are mounted on the back side\nof the PCB, so you can order them fully assembled\n(except for the keys/joystick).\nLEDs need to be mounted flipped, so they shine\nthrough the holes in the board"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 29.845 182.245 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 2.54 2.54)
				(thickness 0.375)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "3b7709b8-3a1b-48e6-8fda-4e587123b164")
	)
	(text "Commodore PET N-type keyboard re-creation with additional, optional features:\n- LED lights per key (controllable by I2C)\n- Keyboard re-mapping (controllable by I2C)\n- New, simpler to use 20-pin IDC connector\n- Diodes to avoid mirroring"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 27.94 38.735 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 2.54 2.54)
				(thickness 0.6)
				(bold yes)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "58626872-dba6-4d64-ae0d-87bd40fa6997")
	)
	(text "Assembly Options:"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 29.21 67.31 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 5.08 5.08)
				(thickness 1.2)
				(bold yes)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "5ff403e4-db50-4e91-9042-affaa4c29fa4")
	)
	(text "RELEASES:\n* N-V1-R1 PCB Submitted 2020-12-18\n* N-V1-R2 PCB Updated 2021-03-31 \n* N-V3-R1 PCB Submitted 2025-10-11\n* PETN-3.1A 2026-01-30"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 133.35 76.2 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 2.0066 2.0066)
				(thickness 0.4013)
				(bold yes)
			)
			(justify left bottom)
		)
		(uuid "7535b9c7-fcf7-40d5-9831-86937639d0e3")
	)
	(text "(C) 2020, 2021 Steve J. Gray\n(C) 2025, 2026 André Fachat"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 248.92 182.118 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 2.54 2.54)
				(thickness 0.508)
				(bold yes)
			)
		)
		(uuid "8ba7a6da-1130-4faa-b4f5-26e54e9a4934")
	)
	(text "R4: 1U x 14\nR3: 1.5U, 1U x 13\nR2: 1.5U, 1U x 11, 1.5U\nR1: 2U, 1U x 10, 2U\nR1: 9U (spacebar)\n* Bottom 2 Rows have\n   same profile on modern\n   keycaps"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 213.36 69.215 0)
		(effects
			(font
